 (a) that to way out the powerful enemy, reciting YAA HASEE-BO 80 times daily is beneficial and effective. If the ritual (amal) starts on Thursday than will get the success soon.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Hazrat Imam Reza (a) se manqool hai keh taaqat-war dushman ko dafa karne ke liye YAA HASEE-BO ko apna vird bana le aur har roz 80 martaba vird kare to mufeed o moassir (asar rakhti) hai. Agar Thursday ke din amal ka aagaaz kare to jald kaamyaab hoga.", "UrduDescription": "حضرت امام رضاؑ سے منقول ہے کہ طاقتور دشمن کو دفع کرنے کے لئے ’’یَاحَسِیْبُ‘‘ کو اپنا ورد بنالے اور ہر روز 80 مرتبہ ورد کرے تو مفید و مؤثر ہے۔ اگر جمعرات کے دن عمل کا آغاز کرے تو جلد کامیاب و غالب ہوگا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "Ara